<h1 id="annotation-editor" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#annotation-editor"><span>Annotation Editor</span></a></h1>
<p>Monorepo for W3C-compliant annotation editing. Provides a NestJS API module for serving annotation definitions, a shared core library for types and validation, and a Vue 3 editor component for creating and managing annotations on text sources.</p>
<h2 id="packages" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#packages"><span>Packages</span></a></h2>
