<p><strong>Supported <code v-pre>fieldInput.type</code> values:</strong> <code v-pre>text</code>, <code v-pre>select</code>, <code v-pre>autocomplete</code></p>
<h4 id="directory-structure" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#directory-structure"><span>Directory Structure</span></a></h4>
<p>Annotation definitions are loaded from a directory where each subfolder represents one annotation type:</p>
<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-"><span class="line"><span>annotations/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>├── person/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   └── resource.json</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>├── place/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   └── resource.json</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>├── event/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   └── resource.json</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>└── _resource/              # optional resource definitions</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>    ├── persons.json</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>    └── places.json</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Each <code v-pre>resource.json</code> contains an <code v-pre>AnnotationJsonConfig</code> object.</p>
<h4 id="frontend-only-usage-no-backend" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#frontend-only-usage-no-backend"><span>Frontend-Only Usage (No Backend)</span></a></h4>
